welcome.title: Welcome & Goodbye
welcome.description: Automatically send messages and give roles to your new members and send a message when a members leaves your server

moderation.title: Moderator
moderation.description: Keep your server safe with auto-moderation & empower your mods with powerful moderation tools

verification.title: Verification
verification.description: Verification gate that your new members need to pass in order to get access to your server.

starboard.title: Starboard
starboard.description: Allows users to react to a message with ⭐️ and send the message to a channel

temporary_channels.title: Temporary Channels
temporary_channels.description: Allow your members to create temporary voice channels in one click in your server

ticketing.title: Ticketing
ticketing.description: Allow your members to submit tickets for support, reports and requests.

leveling.title: Leveling
leveling.description: Give your members XP and Levels when they send messages

birthdays.title: Birthdays
birthdays.description: Track your members birthdays and wish them a happy birthday

giveaway.title: Giveaways
giveaway.description: Launch giveaways and lotteries in your server in one click

economy.title: Economy
economy.description: Players can gain coins everyday. Players can stake their coins in games. Use your coins to buy items from the shop
